<p>This screen is displayed if you have selected the <i>Compose</i> icon
and you have a postponed (unsent) message.</p>

<h2>Using postponed messages</h2>

<ul>
<li> To continue with a postponed message select the <i>Subject</i> 
     field of the relevant message. You will then see the main <i>Compose</i>
     page, with the message presented for further editing.</li>
<li> To start a new message instead, select the <i>Compose a fresh message</i> 
     button.</li>
</ul>

